"{\"uid\": \"tmz.com-2024-08-02-olympic-slovakia-swimmer-tamara-potocka-collapses-medical-emergency-paris\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Frightening moment during the women's 200-meter individual medley qualifying heats at the 2024 Olympics ... when Slovakian swimmerTamara Potockacollapsed poolside after suffering an asthma attack.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old first-time Olympian required immediate medical attention after finishing seventh in the third heat at Paris La D\\u00e9fense Arena on Friday ... with staffers putting her on a stretcher with a neck brace and oxygen mask.\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 225, \"end\": 233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.999966422463182, \"rank\": 3.357799637116558e-05, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka is now being constantly monitored for the next several hours after receiving oxygen and meds, a team rep said in a statement.\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 430, \"end\": 437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tamara has asthma,\\\" Team Slovakia'sIvana Langesaid.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This whole combination of nervous and physical tension while she did not have her inhaler immediately available to use contributed to the creation of this problem.\\\"\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The medical emergency ultimately delayed the next heat of the event ... before the competition eventually resumed.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcers calling the event detailed the atmosphere during Potocka's medical scare ... saying the entire arena went silent, and it appeared to be \\\"very serious.\\\"\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 965, \"end\": 972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka -- who has since been confirmed to be conscious and communicating with medical professionals -- missed the cut for the finals ... finishing with a time of 2:14.20.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes!\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send me email updates and offers from TMZ and its Affiliates.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"score\": 0.9977752929916162, \"rank\": 0.0022296673650811067, \"text\": \"TMZ\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By subscribing, I agree to thePrivacy PolicyandTerms of Use\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": []}]}"